Of course I speak Farsi,

01:32:47.003 --> 01:32:49.466
I wish to make a movie in Iran.

01:33:06.602 --> 01:33:09.031
N—No, I’m… I’m now a writer, and uh…

01:33:10.236 --> 01:33:12.294
Kevin, give me the storyboards.

01:33:12.459 --> 01:33:16.687
These are the drawings that show
what we will film for the movie,

01:33:16.844 --> 01:33:19.362
Alien villains have taken over
the hero’s planet.

01:33:19.602 --> 01:33:22.630
They fight for their families
and take back the city,

01:33:22.712 --> 01:33:25.741
The villains know he is
the chosen one, so,

01:33:25.812 --> 01:33:29.857
they kidnap his son
in the spice market.

01:33:30.785 --> 01:33:33.032
So he and his wife storm the castle.

01:33:33.297 --> 01:33:36.700
The people—hold that…
the people are inspired to join him.

01:33:36.805 --> 01:33:41.223
They are farmers, but they learn to fight.

01:33:44.490 --> 01:33:47.203
They shoot weapons at their enemies.

01:33:49.481 --> 01:33:51.863
And the king of the aliens is destroyed,

01:33:51.864 --> 01:33:53.844
when the people find their courage.

01:34:02.934 --> 01:34:06.323
You don’t go until we verify.

01:34:09.435 --> 01:34:11.853
— I understand.
— Sir…

01:34:12.299 --> 01:34:14.084
Call our office.

01:34:14.202 --> 01:34:15.846
They’ll verify.

01:34:40.677 --> 01:34:42.611
.. It goes all the way
throughout the thirties.

01:34:42.643 --> 01:34:43.414
Hold on pal, we’re shooting.

01:34:43.415 --> 01:34:44.791
We’re just going to the
producer’s building.

01:34:44.830 --> 01:34:47.275
Yeah I understand, I understand
but we’re shooting.

01:35:21.398 --> 01:35:26.049
